        "created_at": "2026-01-26T05:59:58.807Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Am I correct in understanding that if my primary device (the smartphone I used to register) is turned off or Signal is not allowed to run in the background, then the messages I send from my PC are de facto stored for up to the 14-day period?</p>",
